{"tid":1864363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[衛生防護中心更新] 家居檢疫住所由昨24處增至今71處","createTime":"2020-02-05T14:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T14:41:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55d3fcc767234b35a628f0876329ef14c32c9a4a","tid":1864363,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"全港71處居所正有人接受14天家居檢疫<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心更新正接受14天家居檢疫人士的居所名單，由昨日的24處，增加至今日的71處，分布在全港18區。有關人士家居檢疫的最後日期，由今日至下星期四不等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/list_of_buildings_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Flist_of_buildings_tc.pdf&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=d07127fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/list_of_buildings_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRrRbxT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRrRbxT.png&h=a115d767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkC5fZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkC5fZy.png&h=8e75c372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJ8TpST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJ8TpST.png&h=3bc2d069&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e9372811a208593986296d7a3bcb1687a27b163","tid":1864363,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"全港大爆發"},{"pid":"c9180c3c5d5a0fcf9baaf769bba4cf09841884ae","tid":1864363,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ehdpTY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ehdpTY.png&h=b18536a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c85cca1a2712c539d26c290041d40b3d07ce2e8c","tid":1864363,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"